{"id": "1397742558783864854", "channel_id": "1397742558783864854", "type": 0, "author_id": "693983290423509042", "author_name": "climbkaly", "author_bot": false, "content": "I heard that with the 1st anniversary event you had a daily banner in which you could pull for any awakener. I don't know if you are planning to do the same again. I'd like to suggest a story idea for it.\n\nEach day an awakener visits Daffodil's shop and we get to learn more about that awakener.\n\nExamples: \n\nLily comes in looking for a gift for the keeper. Why she selects something reveals something about her character.\n\nGoliath comes in and offers trophy heads to Daffodil. And Daffodil pays him for his services.\n\nPandia comes in looking for a quirky gift for herself.....\n\nAnd you can go on and on with odd interactions that people have in Daffodil's shop. \n\nYou could also provide festival skins....or something.", "timestamp": "2025-07-24T00:49:54.815000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1397742558783864854", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "2nd Anniversary or Christmas Event Suggestion", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "thread_tags": ["1361168939622727801"]}
